metadata.name: Hunt for the Illumirabbit : Runnn!
metadata.description:
Long time a go, there was a sacred, rare, mysterious thing that people all around the galaxy searching for.  Many stories about it has been told.  
Especially the one that claimed it was also a symbolic of a secret ancient organization, so that it called… ‘ The Illumirabbit ’…The glowing sacred rabbit  
We had known that the illumirabbit has only one, but some rumors said “ It’s infinitely ”
